content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #86053 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

This is fuzzer generated, and while it's possible to hit it with valid input, it's not terribly likely. Also an unstable feature. I'd say P-medium? Also F-c_variadic and requires-nightly for other tags.
Agree with P-medium but we can trigger ICE on beta/stable as well so requires-nightly isn't the case
